cypher: Recursive XOR
author: Merle (Marc Wallace)
date:   30 Apr 93
formal: Cypher recurxor("Recursive XOR", encode, decode);


store two random bytes.
set Mask = 0.
for each input I: output (I ^ Mask) (xor) and set Mask = (I ^ Mask).
then store two more random bytes at the end.
to undo, you do basically the same thing.


